Sentencas: La1-xSrxCoO3-delta (LSCO) films have been deposited on LaAlO3 (LAO), La1-xSrxGa1-yMgyO3-delta/LaAlO3 (LSGM/LAO) and yittria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) substrates by pulsed laser deposition (PLD) for application to thin film solid oxide fuel cell cathodes.
Titulo: Structure and conducting properties of La1-xSrxCoO3-δ films

Sentencas: The optimum conditions for deposition were determined for the different substrates in an ambient of 80-310 mTorr oxygen pressure and at a substrate temperature range of 450 to 750 degrees C.
Titulo: Structure and conducting properties of La1-xSrxCoO3-δ films

Sentencas: The films structures were analyzed by XRD, RBS and SEM.
Titulo: Structure and conducting properties of La1-xSrxCoO3-δ films

Sentencas: Epitaxial LSCO films were grown with (110) preferred orientation on YSZ, and with (100) orientation on LAO and LSGM/LAO.
Titulo: Structure and conducting properties of La1-xSrxCoO3-δ films

Sentencas: The electrical resistivity of the epitaxial LSCO films ranged from 10(-2) to 10(-4)
Titulo: Structure and conducting properties of La1-xSrxCoO3-δ films

Sentencas: Ohm cm, depending on the deposition temperature and substrate.
Titulo: Structure and conducting properties of La1-xSrxCoO3-δ films

Sentencas: The ionic conducting behavior of the LSCO film on YSZ was investigated by impedance measurement.
Titulo: Structure and conducting properties of La1-xSrxCoO3-δ films
